CBRE Melbourne Strip Retail Investments are pleased to present to the market, 280 Lygon Street, Brunswick East, for sale via Public On-site Auction Wednesday 13th December at 12:30pm.

We highlight some key points below:

- A high quality 3 level corner building that has been recently renovated to the highest standard providing the eventual purchaser with significant depreciation benefits

- Substantial 877sqm* venue comprising 3 separate entertaining areas including a spacious dining and bar area, an attractive former cellar (operating as an open plan function space) & a second level cocktail bar with balcony overlooking Lygon Street

- Further to the elaborate retail space this exciting opportunity comprises 12 modern and stylish hotel rooms, providing further income potential

- The property is being sold with an existing liquor licence, which includes highly valuable late night (1am) trading

- Major growth forecasted supported by over 1,100 dwellings currently under construction or in planning within 1km, providing higher population density, increased foot traffic and further demand for Brunswick East retailers

*Approx

CBRE Melbourne Strip Retail Investments are pleased to present to the market 157 Lygon Street, Brunswick East, for sale via public on-site auction Wednesday 13th December at 10:30am

We highlight some key features below:

- Leased to longstanding Green Grocer 'Smith & Maloney' providing holding income of $45,000 per annum* with no further options after July 2020

- Set amongst a number of high density residential developments, set to provide a major injection of population in the near future

- Oversized landholding of 244sqm*, with highly accessible rear lane access

- Positioned on an underutilised and flexible allotment, providing the value add potential for future development and/or extension (STCA)

- An exciting freehold opportunity that provides investors, owner occupiers and developers with an unprecedented growth outlook
